message.entry: Invalid Safety Margin. Safety Margin should be real, finite and greater than -100.
Invalid Container Type. Container Type should be a SimulinkFixedPoint.AutoscalerDataTypes
Invalid Comments. Comments should be a cell array.
Invalid isLocked flag. isLocked should be boolean or logical.
Invalid isUnderMask flag. isUnderMask should be boolean or logical.
Invalid default word length. Word length must be an integer in the range [1, 128].
Invalid default fraction length. Fraction length must be an integer in the range [-65536, 65536].
